Sinesis laughs.

"Thanks, new boss!" He said to Megatron. Sinister chuckles and the 2 of them
walk back to base.

"We are so totally rad, now!" Sinister said.

"Yeah, like, I know!" Sinesis said. They laughed.

"Now being serious, now that we are big shots, lets go and eat something and
lounge around!" Sinister said.

"Yeah, whenever Megatron needs us we'll be there." Sinesis said.

"Totally." Sinister replied. They laughed and walked back to base, pleased
to finally be in the Predacons...
